
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-thubert-6tisch-4detnet-01.txt'>
    <title>"6TiSCH requirements for DetNet", Pascal Thubert</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-thubert-6tisch-4detnet-01.txt</link>
    <description>This document builds on the 6TiSCH architecture that defines, among others, mechanisms to establish and maintain deterministic routing and scheduling in a centralized fashion.  The document details dependencies on DetNet and PCE controller to express topologies and capabilities, as well as abstract state that the controller must be able to program into the network devices to enable deterministic forwarding operations.</description>
    <dc:date>2015-06-11T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
